<div class="privacy-policy-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="privacy-policy-container">
      <div class="privacy-content">

        <h2 class="privacy-main-title">Shipping Policy</h2>
        <p class="privacy-paragraph">At <strong>Crafted Charm</strong>, we strive to deliver your handcrafted treasures with care and efficiency. Our shipping policy ensures transparency and convenience throughout your delivery experience.</p>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Domestic Shipping</h3>
        <ul class="privacy-feature-list">
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Shipping Time: <strong>15 to 21 business days</strong> across India</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Standard Delivery Charge: <strong>₹100.00</strong> for orders below ₹2500.00</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Free Shipping: Available on orders above <strong>₹2500.00</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Processing Time</h3>
        <ul class="privacy-feature-list">
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Orders placed Monday–Friday (excluding holidays) process within <strong>2-3 business days</strong></li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Weekend/holiday orders begin processing the next business day</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Pre-order items require <strong>4 weeks</strong> for shipment</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Cash on Delivery (COD)</h3>
        <ul class="privacy-feature-list">
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Available nationwide with convenience fees</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">₹100.00 online booking fee applies to all COD orders</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">COD orders below ₹2500.00 may include additional charges</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Order Tracking</h3>
        <p class="privacy-paragraph">You'll receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking details once your order is dispatched. Track your package in real-time until it reaches your doorstep.</p>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">International Shipping</h3>
        <p class="privacy-paragraph">We currently focus on domestic Indian shipments. For special international requests, please <a href="mailto:craftedcharm.luck@gmail.com" class="contact-email">contact our customer care</a> for customized shipping solutions.</p>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Delivery Assurance</h3>
        <ul class="privacy-feature-list">
          <li class="privacy-list-item">All shipments include insurance for your protection</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Each product is carefully packaged to prevent damage during transit</li>
          <li class="privacy-list-item">Signature required upon delivery for security</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Delivery Updates</h3>
        <p class="privacy-paragraph">While we strive for timely delivery, occasional delays may occur due to weather, holidays, or unforeseen circumstances. We'll promptly notify you if any delays affect your shipment.</p>

        <h3 class="privacy-section-title">Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="privacy-paragraph">For any shipping inquiries, reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:craftedcharm.luck@gmail.com" class="contact-email">craftedcharm.luck@gmail.com</a> or call us at +91 8217719225</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


